TRADE "TRADE SKILL" TRD

(Disambiguation: did you mean HELP TRADE COMMAND or TRADE RELATIONS)

Trade (skill)

The Trade skill contains abilities for collecting, crafting, and trading goods
of all kinds.

You can get started in Trade by crafting things using the Primitive Crafts and
Cook abilities, by chipping flints with rocks to make handaxes, or by tanning
skins into leather.

Many craftable items are scalable, meaning their stats depend on the level of
the person who crafts them. HELP SCALABLE CRAFTS has a full explanation.

You get additional Trade abilities when you reach level 100, depending on
which other skills you have at high levels. Use the 'role' command to choose
which set of skills to use.

See also: CRAFT, IDENTIFY, FORGE, SEWING, POTTERY, WOODWORKING, SHIPBUILDING,
  REFORGE, PRIMITIVE CRAFTS, COOK, ROLE, SKILL, SKILL SYNERGY
