"CRAFT INFO" "FORGE INFO" "SEW INFO" "BUILD INFO" "MANUFACTURE INFO" "COOK INFO"

Usage:  <verb> info <recipe name>

The 'info' subcommand allows you to see specific information on a recipe. This
includes what resources you need for it, what ability it uses, what it creates,
and what else you need for the recipe.

This commmand prioritizes recipes you have the ability for, but can target ones
you don't know. To get crafting information for a pattern recipe, you must have
its pattern in your inventory.

For build, this also shows where you can build the building.
For recipes from patterns, this also shows the level range of the recipe.

See also; RESOURCES, SCALABLE CRAFTS, PATTERNS
