"CUSTOMIZE BUILDING"

Customize Building (Trade ability)

Usage:  customize building name <name | none>
        customize building description <set | none>

Customize Building lets you change the names and descriptions of your build-
ings. You must own the building you're trying to customize, and have permission
from your empire.

When editing a custom description, you can use /fi to add linebreaks and indent
the first line. Generally descriptions look best in the 3-9 line range. You can
use /h to get more information on editor commands, and /s to save and exit.

This ability also allows you to put up roadsigns.

Gain experience by customizing buildings.

See also: STRING EDITOR, ROADSIGN
