"FREE ACTIONS" "CLEAR TERRAIN" "TIDY UP" "SCOUT AREA" "BLOCK WATER" ENGRAVE "MAGIC WORDS" ORGANIZE "SHOVEL SOOT"

Sometimes building or maintaining a building requires you to take certain
actions which have no cost, and just take a few moments to complete. These are
indicated in square brackets, such as [clear terrain], in the list of
resources.

These actions are part of normal building. Type 'build' (or 'maintain') to
start working on the building. Workforce can also perform all of these free
actions.

Note: The [dig] free action should not be confused with the regular 'dig'
command. This digging must be in the correct place, which only happens if you
begin it with the 'build' command.
