Shipbuilding (Trade ability)

Building:  &b~&0()&b~&0  Shipyard (Seafarers goal)
           &b~&0[]&b~&0  Upgraded Shipyard (Great Shipyard goal)
Commands:  manufacture <ship>
           manufacture info <ship>

Ships can be constructed via the manufacture command. This can only be done at
a shipyard, and the vessel can be sailed to a dock when finished. You can also
upgrade the shipyard, if your empire has this knowledge.

You gain experience every time you add resources to a ship being manufactured.

With basic Shipbuilding you can manufacture:
  Caravel
    Type: Exploration ship (shipping)
    Capacity: 150
    Health: 32
    Rooms: 2
  Longship
    Type: Warship (siege weapons)
    Health: 64
    Rooms: 2
  Cog
    Type: Cargo ship (shipping)
    Capacity: 450
    Health: 32
    Rooms: 1

Unlock more advanced ships through empire progression:
  Carrack (exploration, 8 rooms)
  Brigantine (siege, 128 health)
  Hulk (shipping, 1000 capacity)

